title: Mumbai Police
subTitle: ACP Antony Moses has managed to track down his friend's killer when he meets with an accident resulting in partial memory loss. Soon, he is reassigned to investigate the murder and find the culprit.

title: Youth Festival
subTitle: Two classmates, Arjun and Shivan, fall for the same girl, Parvathy, leading to a serious conflict between them over winning her affection.

title: Mizhi Thurakku
subTitle: Savithri's family is attacked, after which she seeks refuge in a man's house. However, she soon experiences the evils of casteism.

title: Orange
subTitle: Yakobi leads a content life with his wife and daughter, working as a lorry driver. However, his life takes a dramatic turn when he encounters his friend Baboottan.

title: Home
subTitle: Oliver Twist, a father yearning to bond with his sons, desperately comes up with ideas to forge a close connection with them.

title: Vismayathumbathu
subTitle: Sreekumar comes across a girl while visiting his childhood friend, Govindan Kutty. However, he later realises that she is the spirit of a student who disappeared a while ago.

title: Lucky Baskhar
subTitle: Desperate to bring his family out of monetary woes, Baskhar Kumar, a bank employee, enters the dangerous and murky world of financial scams.

title: Aavesham
subTitle: Three boys move into a hostel to pursue engineering, where they clash with seniors. To get revenge, they befriend a gangster.

title: Ponman
subTitle: Ajesh, a gold dealer, lends some gold jewelry for a village wedding, unaware of the betrayal ahead. However, the bride's husband plans to keep the gold and kill Ajesh.

title: Baba Kalyani
subTitle: Baba Kalyani, a police officer, travels to Kochi to uncover a terrorist conspiracy. He must not only work on the case but also deal with old rivals who are hell-bent on settling scores with him.

title: Baba Kalyani
subTitle: Baba Kalyani, a police officer, travels to Kochi to uncover a terrorist conspiracy. He must not only work on the case but also deal with old rivals who are hell-bent on settling scores with him.

title: Doctor Love
subTitle: Vinaychandran, a writer, makes a living by selling his average romantic stories. His life takes a turn when he is assumed to be an expert on matters of the heart while trying to help a professor.

title: Thaskara Lahala
subTitle: Three inseparable friends devise an ingenious ploy to fund a destitute woman's marriage. However, destiny plays a cruel game after an unscrupulous individual steal their hard-earned funds.

title: Winter
subTitle: Fed up with the fast-paced city life, Ramdas and his wife decide to move to a quiet bungalow on the outskirts of the city. However, some strange happenings in the surrounding put their lives at risk.

title: Chirikkum Thalika
subTitle: A comprehensive compilation of some of the best rib-tickling comedy scenes from various Malayalam movies featuring renowned actors and actresses.

title: Vellimoonga
subTitle: A middle-aged politician falls in love with a girl who is half his age, only to discover later that she is the daughter of the woman whom he loved in his childhood.

title: Trance
subTitle: Viju, a motivational speaker, is hired to be the face of a religious scam for which he undergoes rigorous training. As his popularity grows, he sinks into the depths of darkness and delusion.

title: Two Countries
subTitle: Ullas schemes to marry Simran, woman with a disability, to avoid repaying a debt, but faces complications when Laya, a wealthy alcoholic, enters his life, turning his plans upside down.

title: Brahmastra
subTitle: With Isha by his side, DJ Shiva rises to a crescendo of love and fortitude to embrace his role as the chosen protector of the universe's most powerful weapon.

title: Padakkalam
subTitle: Four engineering students battle their professor's supernatural schemes to control the campus, encountering cursed gadgets and bizarre scenarios along the way.

title: Grrr...
subTitle: Heartbroken and intoxicated, Rejimon stumbles into a lion's den at the zoo. Haridas, a guard, has to forcefully dive in to rescue him, earning media attention for the blunder.

title: Grrr...

title: Kabali
subTitle: A man spends 25 years in prison for fighting against oppression. Old but still bloodthirsty, he decides to seek revenge against his enemies upon his release.

title: Yugapurushan
subTitle: Sree Narayan Guru is a social reformer who wishes to bring about a change in Kerala. He leads various reform movements to abolish the caste system in his state.

title: Pulival Kalyanam
subTitle: Harikrishnan is an adopted younger brother of Karunan. When Karunan loses his right hand in an accident, Harikrishnan decides to look after his family.

title: Kadha Parayumbol
subTitle: Balan, a barber, struggles to give his family a better living. However, his life changes when his old friend, who is a film star, comes to his village for a film shoot.

title: Pulimurugan
subTitle: A small village seeks help from a man with extraordinary force to protect them against man-eating tigers and the drug mafia.

title: Kantara
subTitle: When greed paves the way for betrayal, scheming and murder, a young tribal reluctantly dons the traditions of his ancestors to seek justice.

title: Bromance
subTitle: When Binto learns of his brother Shinto's disappearance, his search for Shinto leads him to collaborate with others, resulting in unforeseen turns, revelations, and memorable experiences.

title: Johny Johny Yes Appa
subTitle: Johny pretends to be a gentleman but is a thief who thrives on lies and betrayals. His life turns upside down after his encounter with Adam, an orphan.
